name: ui-architect
version: 1.0.0
entry: SKILL.md
description: >
  Composition-first premium frontend builder. Produces production-grade React/HTML UI
  by walking a structured pipeline: classify → source (shadcn → curated library → live
  lookup → custom) → tokenize → assemble → QA. Covers landing pages, SaaS dashboards,
  admin panels, pricing pages, auth flows, and financial/trading UI.
triggers:
  - build me a UI
  - make a dashboard
  - design a landing page
  - create a pricing page
  - make it look premium
  - make it look professional
  - use shadcn
  - make it look like Stripe
  - make it look like Linear
  - make it look like Vercel
  - React component
  - build a page
references:
  - references/component-decision-tree.md
  - references/design-system.md
  - references/marketing-components.md
  - references/app-components.md
  - references/live-lookup-and-qa.md
output_modes:
  - artifact       # single .jsx in-chat render, default
  - full_project   # scaffolded repo with package.json, tailwind config, etc.
